{"tid":420001,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我終於明白黃子華點解話一個笑話唔掂，會慘過俾雷劈","createTime":"2017-10-01T04:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T06:19:20.000Z","uid":89189,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2b0540b7dce261a0763553e2c1c8b2671ccbe1","tid":420001,"uid":89189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:33:36.000Z","msg":"成班freerider唔撚做野都算，仲要推我上台死，雖然我自問做presentation嘅功力都幾深厚，但當我行上到台，已經感受到幾百人一齊放出前所未有嘅逼力，正面迎擊咁強大嘅氣場只會令人體爆炸，為咗令氣氛冇咁緊張，我就決定先講我之前諗定嘅笑話。<br />\n<br />\n「正所謂台上一分鐘，台下十年功，假如我present咗十分鐘，即係有一百年嘅功力啦，哈哈哈.....」<br />\n<br />\n結果由熱鬧嘅氣氛瞬間變到全場都靜哂，個一刻我就好似真係俾雷一嘢劈落天靈蓋咁，霎時之間，我靈光一閃，我講咗句<br />\n<br />\n「各位同學，知唔知點解1+1等於2啊？因為蟻多嬲死象啊，哈哈」<br />\n<br />\n依然冇人出聲<br />\n<br />\n我大叫一聲：「你老豆都冇飛，噗，噗，噗」<br />\n<br />\n係個刻，我已經知道，我正式變成一個超級大傻仔，我直頭想人體爆炸死咗去就算，當自己唔存在。雖然大家都有笑到，但係我知道佢地根本唔係笑緊嗰個唔似笑話嘅笑話，而係笑我好柒。<br />\n個種孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個種寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個種無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試問誰又能承受得到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人有類似嘅經驗？"},{"pid":"58a2cb42ae1b02eec5e3009d681f5e8a800b1e3c","tid":420001,"uid":104454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:39:21.000Z","msg":"希望樓主只係作故仔<br />\n<br />\n真係唔敢相信有人現實可以柒到咁"},{"pid":"d5d43877c280c9623ae8c6566c2b9f435cf4064e","tid":420001,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望樓主只係作故仔<br />\n<br />\n真係唔敢相信有人現實可以柒到咁</blockquote><br />\n真係好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78bac63edaa506068eb5d654b5e58305ad19e23a","tid":420001,"uid":17232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望樓主只係作故仔<br />\n<br />\n真係唔敢相信有人現實可以柒到咁</blockquote><br />\n呢個故仔都作得好撚柒"},{"pid":"0d1ee0a3fea9467435db61c3b1b3d8a8975c3e39","tid":420001,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"求神拜佛冇人拍你片<br />\n唔係你就會係第二個阿輝"},{"pid":"23cda24a519dcd2d317990c3712730a2fb8363a0","tid":420001,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:54:18.000Z","msg":"入呢個post慘過俾雷劈"},{"pid":"10fe62eefbcdaf4af5de8997280e26002b8c50b6","tid":420001,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:04:04.000Z","msg":"尷尬"},{"pid":"7e362432e98d8695a0f846373b13a86b67ec428b","tid":420001,"uid":89189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:05:28.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以柒過我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fce3256a0948e3e438fa3780f4fbd511fb5d879","tid":420001,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"........"},{"pid":"dc49b3619fef16ceae11fc8f4952341d1dbc770f","tid":420001,"uid":89189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:19:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>希望樓主只係作故仔<br />\n<br />\n真係唔敢相信有人現實可以柒到咁</blockquote><br />\n真係好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒到盡頭便是型<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}